*Račune* su nam izdali u roku od mesec dana. (The invoices were issued to us within a month.)

Nismo još platili *račune* za prošlu godinu. (We haven't yet paid the bills for last year.)

Kako ćemo platiti *račune* ako nemamo novca? (How are we going to pay the bills if we don't have any money?)

Treba da se obratimo banci da bismo mogli da platimo *račune*. (We need to turn to the bank in order to pay the bills.)

Ne možemo da platimo *račune* ako nemamo dovoljno novca. (We can't pay the bills if we don't have enough money.)